problem_text: Diamond Mine is a professional wrestling stable, formed in WWE. Roderick Strong leads Diamond Mine. Diamond Mine includes the Creed Brothers, and Ivy Nile. Imperium has a feud with Diamond Mine.
predicates:
ProfessionalWrestlingStable(x) ::: x is a professional wrestling stable.
FormedIn(x, y) ::: x is formed in y.
Leads(x, y) ::: x leads y.
Includes(x, y) ::: x includes y.
Feud(x, y) ::: x has a feud with y.
DiamondMine(x) ::: x is Diamond Mine.
RoderickStrong(x) ::: x is Roderick Strong.
WWE(x) ::: x is WWE.
CreedBrothers(x) ::: x is the Creed Brothers.
IvyNile(x) ::: x is Ivy Nile.
Imperium(x) ::: x is Imperium.

tests.questions: Based on the above information, is the following statement true or false? Roderick Strong leads a professional wrestling stable that was formed in WWE.
tests.conclusions: Leads(roderickStrong, diamondMine) ∧ FormedIn(diamondMine, wwe) ::: Roderick Strong leads a professional wrestling stable that was formed in WWE. TRUE

tests.questions: Based on the above information, is the following statement true or false? The Creed Brothers are part of a professional wrestling stable that has a feud with Imperium.
tests.conclusions: ∃x ∃y (Includes(x, creedbrothers) ∧ Feud(x, imperium)) ::: The Creed Brothers are part of a professional wrestling stable that has a feud with Imperium. TRUE

tests.questions: Based on the above information, is the following statement true or false? Ivy Nile is part of a professional wrestling stable that has a feud with Imperium.
tests.conclusions: ∃x ∃y (IvyNile(x) ∧ Includes(y, x) ∧ Feud(y, Imperium)) ::: Ivy Nile is part of a professional wrestling stable that has a feud with Imperium. FALSE

tests.questions: Based on the above information, is the following statement true or false? Imperium has a feud with a professional wrestling stable that includes the Creed Brothers and Ivy Nile.
tests.conclusions: ∃x ∃y ∃z (ProfessionalWrestlingStable(x) ∧ Feud(Imperium, x) ∧ Includes(x, y) ∧ Includes(x, z) ∧ CreedBrothers(y) ∧ IvyNile(z)) ::: TRUE

tests.questions: Based on the above information, is the following statement true or false? Diamond Mine is a professional wrestling stable that includes the Creed Brothers and Ivy Nile and has a feud with Imperium.
tests.conclusions: DiamondMine(x) ∧ FormedIn(x, WWE) ∧ Includes(x, CreedBrothers) ∧ Includes(x, IvyNile) ∧ Feud(Imperium, x) ::: Diamond Mine is a professional wrestling stable that includes the Creed Brothers and Ivy Nile and has a feud with Imperium. FALSE

tests.questions: Based on the above information, is the following statement true or false? Diamond Mine is a professional wrestling stable that is led by Roderick Strong and has a feud with Imperium.
tests.conclusions: (DiamondMine(x) ∧ ProfessionalWrestlingStable(x) ∧ Leads(x, roderickstrong) ∧ Feud(x, imperium)) ::: Diamond Mine is a professional wrestling stable that is led by Roderick Strong and has a feud with Imperium. FALSE

tests.questions: Based on the above information, is the following statement true or false? Roderick Strong leads Diamond Mine, and Diamond Mine includes Ivy Nile.
tests.conclusions: Leads(roderickStrong, diamondMine) ∧ Includes(diamondMine, ivyNile) ::: Roderick Strong leads Diamond Mine, and Diamond Mine includes Ivy Nile. TRUE

tests.questions: Based on the above information, is the following statement true or false? Roderick Strong leads a professional wrestling stable that was formed in WWE and has a feud with Imperium.
tests.conclusions: Leads(roderickstrong, diamondmine) ∧ FormedIn(diamondmine, wwe) ∧ Feud(imperium, diamondmine) ::: Roderick Strong leads a professional wrestling stable that was formed in WWE and has a feud with Imperium. TRUE

tests.questions: Based on the above information, is the following statement true or false? Roderick Strong leads a professional wrestling stable that is formed in WWE.
tests.conclusions: Leads(roderickStrong, diamondMine) ∧ FormedIn(diamondMine, wwe) ::: Roderick Strong leads a professional wrestling stable that is formed in WWE. TRUE

tests.questions: Based on the above information, is the following statement true or false? Diamond Mine is a professional wrestling stable formed in WWE, and Roderick Strong leads Diamond Mine, which includes the Creed Brothers and Ivy Nile.
tests.conclusions: DiamondMine(x) ∧ FormedIn(x, WWE) ∧ Leads(RoderickStrong, x) ∧ Includes(x, CreedBrothers) ∧ Includes(x, IvyNile) ::: TRUE
